(523, 'https://www.topcv.vn/viec-lam/back-end-developer-nodejs-javascript-mongodb/375749.html?ta_source=JobSearchList', 'Back-End Developer (Nodejs, JavaScript, Mongodb)', 'Hà Nội', 'ha-noi', 'Tầng 9, Toàn nhà Erowindow, số 2 Tôn Thất Tùng, Đống Đa, Hà Nội', 'Toàn thời gian', 'Nhân viên', 'Git,Javascript,MongoDB,NodeJS', NULL, 20000000, NULL, 41, 34, ' 1. General requirements:\n  - Computer science degree or equivalent experience\n  - 1 year or more of experience Javascript, Node JS  - Strong analysis and problem-solving skills.\n  - Ability to work independently or with a group\n   2. Job requirements:\n  - Fluency or understanding of TypeScript (prioritize who have used and experienced in Golang, Rust)\n  - Experience with NodeJS (fresher > 6 months, junior > 1 year, senior > 2 years)\n  - Fluency application development principles through API and microservice architecture, load balancing, gateway, event sourcing, etc.\n  - In-depth understanding of basic to distributed databases such as MongoDB, SQL, Redis.\n  - Experience in using message brokers systems: zmq, kafka ...\n  - Fluency in source and project management tools like Git, Github; writing API documentation and tools for code quality control and API documentation.\n  - Ability to self-learn and suggest changes to improve application performance. '),
